    "Figure 7a is the correlation coefficient between polarity scores of companies before ET processing and Figure 7b is the correlation coefficient of features output by ET.",
    "These two figures were generated using all the training data.",
    "Based on the experimental results, after ET processing, the correlation between the sentiment features of different companies is generally stronger, with more cells showing yellow or green shades.",
    "This improvement is likely due to ET's ability to capture inter-company interactions, which helps to infer and fill in missing sentiment data for certain companies.",
    "This is one of the key motivations behind its design."
